# Nebutra-Sailor — Windsurf / Cascade Rules

## Project Identity

**Nebutra-Sailor** is an enterprise-grade SaaS monorepo for AI-native, multi-tenant platforms.

Stack: Next.js 16 (App Router, Turbopack) · Hono · Prisma v7 · Clerk · Tailwind v4 · TypeScript 5.9 · Biome · Vitest · Playwright · Turborepo · pnpm 10.32+

